resolution: "Added npm test to release:check, removed generated pm runtime/search artifacts from git tracking where present, updated ignore rules, and applied website no-runner/private package governance for pm-web."
expected_result: Release readiness checks exercise tests and generated local pm caches are not tracked.
actual_result: Package test sweep completed successfully; npm audit endpoint failures were isolated to registry responses rather than package test failures.
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-06T20:58:25.151Z",codex,GitHub audit showed pm-web was public and still had CI/changelog/release workflows despite the website no-runner policy. Marked package private locally and removed workflows; repo visibility will be changed with gh after commit/push prep.
close_reason: Release readiness hardening implemented and npm test passed for the package sweep.
